== Usage ==

* Use cabal install to build the implementation
* Exectute ''haskellSnap -p 8010''' to start the server
Both steps are covered by a ''Makefile'' with a target ''run''. 
* Open [http://localhost:8010/Company/View] to demo, starting with the root view.
* Use Ctrl+C to interrupt the server.
* Use the target ''clean'' to "reset" the project. 


